timing_aocv_derate_mode(25.10)                  timing_aocv_derate_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_aocv_derate_mode

Syntax
        timing_aocv_derate_mode

       {aocv_multiplicative | aocv_additive}

       Default: aocv_multiplicative

       Controls the AOCV derating mode.

       When set to aocv_multiplicative, the derating factor will be calculated
       as AOCV derating * OCV derating, which is set using the set_timing_der-
       ate command.

       When  set  to  aocv_additive, the derating factor will be calculated as
       AOCV derating + OCV derating values.

       When you use this global variable, the report_timing command shows  the
       total_derate  column  in  the timing report output, which allows you to
       view and cross-check the calculated total derate factor.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

